🌟 Features
🔐 User Authentication

Login and logout functionality using Redux.

Authentication state persisted in local storage.

Tasks are protected behind authentication.

📝 Task Management

Add new tasks via a user-friendly input form.

View all tasks in a structured list format.

Delete individual tasks with a single click.

Assign priority to tasks (High, Medium, Low).

Categorize tasks as Indoor or Outdoor.

🌦️ Weather Integration

Integrated OpenWeatherMap API to fetch real-time weather data.

For every Outdoor task, the current weather conditions are displayed next to the task.

Graceful error handling for failed API calls or network issues.

💾 Persistent Data

Tasks and authentication status are saved in Local Storage.

Tasks remain saved even after page reload or browser restart.

🧠 Advanced State Management

Uses Redux Toolkit for centralized and scalable state management.

Redux Thunk used to handle asynchronous operations like API calls.

🧩 React Functional Components & Hooks

Built using React functional components.

Makes extensive use of useState, useEffect, useDispatch, useSelector.

📱 Responsive Design

Designed with mobile-first approach.

Fully responsive layout using CSS Flexbox and CSS Grid.

Works seamlessly across mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

✨ Enhanced UI/UX

Clean and minimal UI with easy navigation.

Snackbar or alert messages for task actions like add/delete/login.

Neatly organized project folder structure with scalable codebase.
